<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
There are several things bogus about your tests. First, What you're not realizing is that the increased chance of landing a spell is against the secondary check. It doesn't do you any good to have the second check when the first one fails(checks MR then chr). Second We all know the BS with the random number generator in EQ. You do a test with 1000 runs of each and then we'll look at the numbers. Third, chr may well indeed have no effect in PvP but that doesn't discount it's effectiveness in PvE.
</FONT>
