<HR size="1" color="#dedfdf">
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Interesting test in the PVP enviroment. I would expect it to have those kinds of results. PVP tends to follow different laws than normal mob combat.<P>I will continue to keep my charisma pretty high however. I have tried using the low charisma vs the high charisma and found a vast difference in resists.  <P>To each his own. I suppose as long as I do my job and keep the restless monsters standing around to be killed my group wont care if my charisma is 50 or 300.<P>I also noted that I am able to keep creatures charmed for vastly longer periods of time with a high charisma.  I had a nice wizard pet the other night for around 7 minutes. <P>My stats are:<BR>39th level HE<BR>Charisma 189<BR>Int 160<P>Enjoy.<BR>-Rezek<BR>P.S. Humans level faster? 8)
